Installation instructions for library hppDoc
----------------------------------------------

It is recommended to create a specific directory to install this package.
mkdir build
cd build
../configure [OPTIONS]
make 
make install

If you install from git, you need to access two submodules. To do so, add the
following lines in your ~/.gitconfig:

[url "git://roboptim.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/roboptim/"
     insteadOf = roboptim:
[url "ssh://[softs|git].laas.fr/git/"] 
     insteadOf = git-laas:

where [softs|git] means
  - git if you are an external user,
  - softs if you are a member of CNRS-LAAS.
